<item>
            <title>[OAK-1330] Impersonation doesn&apos;t set Session attributes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-1330</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Jackrabbit used to copy attributes from Credentials to the Session object.&lt;br/&gt;
Sling is reading ResourceResolver.USER_IMPERSONATOR attribute from the session.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;OAK doesn&apos;t set those sessions attributes anymore.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
