                            <comment id="13873208" author="anchela" created="Thu, 16 Jan 2014 09:58:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;i hoped that we could get rid of copying over the attributes from the credentials to the session as this looks more like a bug to me.&lt;br/&gt;
will see what we can do to ensure backwards compatibility&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13873522" author="anchela" created="Thu, 16 Jan 2014 15:54:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;in fact we don&apos;t have to do that in the Repository. the attributes are already populated in the login module, but didn&apos;t properly handle impersonation credentials. while fixing this i additionally addressed an issue with respect to token generation and attribute handling.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
